title: Introducing Gillette Venus Naked Skin® designed by Braun
description: Introducing a new at-home hair removal solution derived from professional Intense Pulsed Light technology. The Gillette Venus Naked Skin® designed by Braun Intense Pulsed Light Hair Removal System helps break the cycle of hair re-growth, and you could experience noticeable hair reduction after six treatments.  Continuously Smooth.  Continuously Beautiful.
